## Description {#details}

Our current alias analysis API differentiates heavily between calls and non-calls, and functions called on one usually assert on the other.

This class encapsulates the distinction to simplify other code that wants &quot;Memory affecting instructions and related data&quot; to use as a key. For example, this class is used as a densemap key in the use optimizer.
